com.yworks.yfiles.layout

Class YGraphAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.YGraphAdapter

  • public class YGraphAdapter
extends Object
    Converts an IGraph instance into a Graph instance.

    This class creates a structural copy of a given IGraph and provides convenience methods to convert items from one graph instance to their corresponding item in the other graph instance.

    The main use case of this class is executing one of the analysis algorithms on an IGraph, for example ShortestPaths, Cycles, and Centrality. For executing a layout algorithm, use the convenience class LayoutExecutor, the convenience methods IGraph.applyLayout(ILayoutAlgorithm, LayoutData) and GraphControl.morphLayout(ILayoutAlgorithm, java.time.Duration, com.yworks.yfiles.utils.IEventHandler), or LayoutGraphAdapter.

    See Also:
    LayoutGraphAdapter, LayoutExecutor, Bipartitions, Centrality, Cycles, GraphChecker, GraphConnectivity, Groups, IndependentSets, NetworkFlows, NodeOrders, Paths, RankAssignments, ShortestPaths, SpanningTrees, Transitivity, Trees

      • YGraphAdapter

        public YGraphAdapter(IGraph originalGraph)
        Initializes a new instance of the YGraphAdapter class.

        This will create a copy of the originalGraph that has the same structure and makes it available via the YGraph property.

        Parameters:
        originalGraph - The original graph whose structure will be copied.

        public final <K,V> IDataMap createDataMap(Class<K> kType,
                                          Class<V> vType,
                                          IMapper<K,V> mapper)
        Creates an IDataMap that delegates to the provided IMapper when queried for items in the YGraph.

        This method is useful where algorithms require IDataMaps as input and that input can be obtained from IMapper instances that provide and accept values for the original nodes and edges.

        Type Parameters:
        K - The type of the keys in the mapper.
        V - The type of the values in the mapper.
        Parameters:
        vType - The type of the values in the mapper.
        kType - The type of the keys in the mapper.
        mapper - The mapper to direct requests to.
        Returns:
        An IDataMap that will delegate the functionality to the mapper.
        See Also:
        createDataProvider(Class, IMapper)
